original_font_information.description:
The first version of Vazir was based on DejaVu 2.35 (was committed to the public domain) to begin designing and developing this new typeface.
Non-Arabic (Latin) glyphs and data are imported from Roboto font (version 2.137; 2017) under the Apache License, Version 2.0.
